 Reviewed-by: Oleg Drokin &amp;lt;green@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;diff --git a/lustre/tests/sanity.sh b/lustre/tests/sanity.sh&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
